{"tid":2217293,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家覺得有幾多公務員會宣誓效忠黨？","createTime":"2020-09-25T10:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T11:25:28.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d1f8d07e3a1972b5998d830596579ea7dcc3c96","tid":2217293,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"政府擬下月要求7.1後入職公務員簽署擁護基本法聲明<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長聶德權表示，正諮詢公務員團體有關現職公務員宣誓的意見。他表示，如果公務員於網絡的私人言行，被人公開之後又惹人質疑，當局會小心審視，有否違反誓言。聶德權又說，計劃下月向各政府部門發出通告，要求今年7月1日後入職的公務員，簽署擁護《基本法》及效忠香港特區的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n2020-09-25 18:13:11<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔計7.1 後入職一定要， 保守估計92.7%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7409d6377b9840b91224e0f7ee3268354c979446","tid":2217293,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"100"},{"pid":"4411d937d5b537fb15475107805e890e1e423b1b","tid":2217293,"uid":173184,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"All"},{"pid":"eb3d042601e60dd2a9d7d9ae9b6dd3e36ebe60a7","tid":2217293,"uid":80610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"100"},{"pid":"83ad44235300ea02d2210bc4d7fed7cce46e6b31","tid":2217293,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4411d937d5b537fb15475107805e890e1e423b1b","tid":2217293,"uid":173184,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"All"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"分化狗，公務員都有手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77fc9091e2662e9c00eec071467a58de9154585","tid":2217293,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"唔宣誓無得撈<br />\n即係會離職<br />\n所以只會公佈１００％既人宣誓效忠<br />\n點會同你講有幾多人因為唔宣誓而離職<br />\n<br />\n呢個PO真係好垃圾<br />\n分化PO拉"},{"pid":"86e999185dc34e9da1b9b962eedeef123edbb4c7","tid":2217293,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike"